description:
Fran sets out with a party to tackle the Spider`s Nest, but one party member isn`t convinced she deserves her rank. A friendly duel will set the record straight.
Source: HIDIVE

titles.title: Abenteurer von Rang A sind Bestien
L`aventurière de rang A est monstrueuse
Rank A Boukensha wa Bakemono Deshita
ランクA冒険者はバケモノでした
